168
00:10:08,549 --> 00:10:11,030
- To find—
- For hotpot.

169
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:13,089
I'm heading to the Old Town, too. Hop in.

170
00:10:13,089 --> 00:10:14,389
Please give us a lift.

171
00:10:14,389 --> 00:10:15,790
Come on.

172
00:10:18,690 --> 00:10:20,690
Granny, be careful.

173
00:10:20,690 --> 00:10:22,799
Fasten your seat belt. Come on.

174
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:24,590
Let me help you.

175
00:10:24,590 --> 00:10:26,270
Sit tight.

176
00:10:41,030 --> 00:10:42,599
