178
00:10:43,699 --> 00:10:45,760
You can use the one in my bag.

179
00:10:45,760 --> 00:10:47,140
Okay.

180
00:10:53,810 --> 00:10:56,270
- Did you rent this car?
- Yeah.

181
00:10:56,270 --> 00:10:59,839
